Are you also suspicious of Yun Qingxuan?

5
00:01:22,680 --> 00:01:23,200
Yes.

6
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,280
But also no.

7
00:01:25,719 --> 00:01:27,280
In the whole Peach Blossom Manor,

8
00:01:27,640 --> 00:01:29,640
only Yun Qingxuan is close to us.

9
00:01:30,280 --> 00:01:32,840
And she's been helping us investigate the case.

10
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:35,239
How could she possibly be the culprit?

11
00:01:36,599 --> 00:01:38,120
Isn't that exactly the problem?

12
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,959
From the very beginning,

13
00:01:41,760 --> 00:01:42,560
including the autopsy,

14
00:01:42,879 --> 00:01:43,879
to providing clues,

15
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:45,599
and even helping us deduce the case,

16
